{"id": 1211, "genre": 1001, "title": "一个人出门旅游的时候，你都遇到过哪些麻烦事？", "description": "然而，傲娇的我，并不想寻找（能找到）旅伴。（题图来自：John Devolle）", "record_count": 2578, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160908171110jDoSxVdbsfFz15Qe.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-10T17:00:58Z", "options": [{"id": 114945, "content": "行李存在车站，而行李柜打不开了，火车还15分钟就要开了..", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 317223}, {"id": 114946, "content": "匆忙到了站台，结果上错车了，也因此错过了熊本最后一趟开往别府的列车，还坐反了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 317223}, {"id": 114947, "content": "想来最大的麻烦也就是 你想吃个什么大点的菜 一个人真的只能放弃?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 552870}, {"id": 114949, "content": "时不时会引发周遭人好奇的目光，琢磨这人一个人有什么可玩的？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 754673}, {"id": 114951, "content": "睡觉害怕", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 751973}, {"id": 115719, "content": "行李带太多，想走的地方太多，钱太少", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 757796}, {"id": 114952, "content": "想找个地方买杯水，架不住自己拖着大包小包，排着长队的痛苦", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 754677}, {"id": 130057, "content": "来大姨妈一个人在青旅床上疼的死去活来……没个同伴能递杯热水?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 208642}, {"id": 114954, "content": "自拍相机没摆稳摔到地上，陌生人都看不下去说我来帮你拍吧，于是特不好意思地摆拍了游客照就匆匆谢过对方（明明自己刚才想拍得更佳有张力一点啊，可是实在不好意思拒绝对方热情的帮忙）", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 754681}, {"id": 117770, "content": "找不到厕所。问路人时，有人会找错路～", "image": "img/option/option/20160920103843BfDOnJCxim4l1TRw", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 758518}, {"id": 114957, "content": "自己一个人人生地不熟，不知道哪的东西好吃和该做哪些事", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 754702}, {"id": 121615, "content": "听到隔壁啪啪啪的声音？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 783228}, {"id": 114962, "content": "买电影票被白眼儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 745219}, {"id": 114963, "content": "不想从融入当地生活的心境中走出来的时候，有点烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749635}, {"id": 114965, "content": "酒店住便宜的", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699923}, {"id": 114968, "content": "没有自拍杆却想要拍照留念", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696973}, {"id": 114971, "content": "没有艳遇 抱着期待出门 失望而归", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117603}, {"id": 114972, "content": "一顿饭不能上饭店吃，因为只能点一个菜，没办法尝试更多的菜色。在咖啡厅或者饭馆，想上厕所却没人帮忙看着位子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749156}, {"id": 118812, "content": "突然就很容易相信陌生人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770032}, {"id": 114973, "content": "地铁坐反了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 746105}, {"id": 114974, "content": "没人陪好吧……所有的问题有多一个人在身边基本都能解决", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 752923}, {"id": 114209, "content": "住酒店的钱没人share，买旅行产品还要补单人差价", "image": null, "praise_count": 206, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 114977, "content": "被强制消费", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 741695}, {"id": 114210, "content": "在机场火车站拖着大包小包的行李，都不想去上厕所了", "image": null, "praise_count": 649, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 114978, "content": "最怕①個人吃飯，啥都想吃，卻只能吃快餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 754795}, {"id": 114211, "content": "出去吃饭能选的地方都很有限，去个小吃街也只能尝一两种", "image": null, "praise_count": 331, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 114212, "content": "自拍杆完全没办法拍到我身后的蓝天草原，沮丧", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 114980, "content": "丢了东西无处可以找回", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 722134}, {"id": 114213, "content": "在机场过夜，又想睡又怕东西丢，尝试过把头发绑在行李箱上", "image": null, "praise_count": 178, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 114982, "content": "吃饭的时候总是不能吃大餐，因为一个人吃太贵", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 546392}, {"id": 114983, "content": "发现当地手机卡无法上网", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 754826}, {"id": 115495, "content": "拖拉行李！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 756428}, {"id": 119847, "content": "没人知道自己的落寞", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 774455}, {"id": 114984, "content": "想去蹲坑 可是不知道行李箱怎么办？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632255}, {"id": 116264, "content": "去宾馆开房时空着一张床。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759459}, {"id": 116266, "content": "吃饭时点一个嫌少点两个吃不完。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759459}, {"id": 114987, "content": "你们说的都对，但我还是选择一个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 99741}, {"id": 114989, "content": "完全！不！知！道！自己要去哪里！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 521582}, {"id": 114991, "content": "话痨一个人旅游自言自语了一天?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 317225}, {"id": 114992, "content": "怎么拍都没一个完整的自己 一场旅行下来 差不多全是风景图 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 754857}, {"id": 114995, "content": "在陌生城市就像一个流浪者，不知何去何从。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 509419}, {"id": 114998, "content": "三个人出去玩 其中两个人闹变扭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 735076}, {"id": 114999, "content": "上完厕所突然发现落东西了，没办法，只好回去找", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748874}, {"id": 115000, "content": "无人聊天，喝酒没伴。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 754908}, {"id": 115003, "content": "错过飞机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 531050}, {"id": 115004, "content": "吃饭不能点太多，但总是想尝多一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 739156}, {"id": 115005, "content": "邮寄火车票，结果到酒店找不到火车票了，第二天就要走了，急死仙人！结果被总台小哥给放私人抽屉里，休假去了！总台英文不通所以无限沟通了好大一阵子，幸好是最后搞明白了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 754916}, {"id": 121661, "content": "一个人 上厕所 不方便 \n拍照 手机没有电", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 730567}, {"id": 115006, "content": "一个人拖着大包小包不敢在火车上饭店里让别人看包去上厕所。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672235}, {"id": 117568, "content": "手机没电，还不认识路", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689377}]}